<template>Show {{ post.value[0].by }}</template>
<script setup>
import { ref, onMounted, onRenderTriggered } from "vue";
import axios from "axios";
const post = ref([]);
onRenderTriggered(() => {
  axios
    .get("https://hacker-news.firebaseio.com/v0/item/126809.json?print=pretty")
    .then((response) => {
      post.value.push(response.data);
      console.log(post.value);
    })
    .catch((error) => {
      console.error("Error fetching data:", error);
    });
});

</script>
